    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Shakuton Clan, Level 4+</p><p>The motes of flame you manifest increase in intensity. <br />You gain the following Benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Increase your Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p><p><br />• Your Scorch Die increase in size by 1 Step. <br />(D4&gt;D6&gt;D8&gt;D10&gt;D12)</p><p> </p><p>• When you would cast Scorch Release: Scorching Murder, increase the number of motes you create by an amount equal to the rank it was cast at. <br />(D-Rank/C-Rank: 1, B-Rank/A-Rank: 2, S-Rank: 3)</p>",
